/profesiastatic.sk/images/design_resp/design/blank.png\" alt=\"Hľadať\" class=\"ico search-nosprite\" /></form><script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\tjQuery(document).ready(function(){\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEnlargeInputWidth(\"#header #search\", \"#header .search\", 1.8);\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tInitFulltextAutocompleter(\"#fulltextsearch #search\");\n\t\t\t\t\t\t});\n\t\t\t\t\t\n// -->\n</script>\n</div><div class=\"show-on-phones\"><a title=\"Hľadajte ponuky práce podľa rôznych kritérií\" href=\"/search.php\"><img src=\"http://profesiastatic.sk/images/design_resp/icons/ico_search_big_nosprite.png\" alt=\"Hľadajte ponuky práce podľa rôznych kritérií\" width=\"27\" height=\"27\" /></a></div></div><div class=\"row-header-favorite\"><div class=\"header-favorite\"><a  title=\"Moje vybrané pracovné ponuky\" class=\"ico-shopping-cart-toppanel\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"/user_details.php?action=show_my_offers&amp;ref_top_panel=157\">6</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"content\"><div class=\"row\">\n    <div class=\"sixteen columns\">\n\t<div class=\"space-on-sides\">\n\t    <ul class=\"breadcrumbs\" ><li><a href=\"/user_details.php\">Moje konto</a></li><li class=\"show-on-phones\"><a onclick=\"$('.path-hide-on-phones').toggleClass('hide-on-phones'); $(this).parent().hide(); return false;\" href=\"#\">...</a></li><li class=\"path-hide-on-phones hide-on-phones\"><a href=\"/praca/\">Hľadanie práce</a></li><li><span class=\"current\"> UX Designer </span></li></ul>\n\t</div>\n    </div>\n</div>\t\t    <!-- C2_CT_R detail CV -->\n\t\t    \t\t    <div class=\"row\">\n\t\t    \t<div class=\"space-on-sides\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"detail\" class=\"eleven columns\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/JobPosting\"><h1 itemprop=\"title\"> UX Designer </h1><h2 itemprop=\"hiringOrganization\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\"><span itemprop='name' class=\"normal\">NESS KDC, s.r.o.</span></h2><div class=\"line-separator\"></div><div class='maintextearea'><div class=\"subtitle-line\"><a name=\"section1\" ></a><h3>Information about the position</h3></div><div class=\"panel infopanel\"><ul   class=\"top-box\" ><li><b>Place of work:</b> <span  itemprop=\"jobLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Place\">Business Center Moldavská, Moldavská 10/B, Košice</span></li><li><b>Start date:</b> ASAP</li><li><b>Contract type:</b> <span  itemprop=\"employmentType\">full-time</span></li></ul></div><dl class=\"details\"><dt>Job description, responsibilities and duties</dt><dd>For our new client, Europe´s leading mobile resource management provider specialising in Vehicle & Asset Tracking, Mobile Workforce Applications and Microsoft Dynamics CRM and ERP software, we are looking for a skilled Ux professional. <br />\n• Keep the interface beautiful and easy to use. <br />\n• Direct the visual appearance of all new features and enhancements on our software application<br />\n• Initiate, suggest, and spearhead major UI re-factorings for a more intuitive user-experience<br />\n• Design elegant solutions to complex workflows. Design things that people will talk about<br />\n• Act as “go to” with in-depth knowledge of user interface best practices and standards. <br />\nUse research-related services, theories and methods to support your recommendations</dd></dl><div class=\"subtitle-line\"><a name=\"section2\" ></a><h3>Requirements for the employee</h3></div><dl class=\"details\"><dt>Minimum education required</dt><dd>Secondary with school-leaving examination<br /><br /><b>Candidates with the following education also suit the position:</b><br />Follow-up/Higher Professional Education<br />University education (Bachelor's degree)<br />University education (Master's degree)<br />Postgraduate (Doctorate)<br /></dd><dt>Skills</dt><dd><strong>Language skills:</strong><br />English - advanced<br /><br /><strong>Computer skills - programmer:</strong><br />JavaScript - advanced<br />HTML - advanced<br />CSS - advanced</dd><dt>Personality requirements and skills</dt><dd>• Adobe Creative Suite - advanced<br />\n• Visio/Balsamiq - intermediate<br />\n• HTML - intermediate<br />\n• CSS - intermediate<br />\n• Strong written and oral communication skills<br />\n• Strong problem solving skills<br />\n• Teamwork skills <br />\n• Ability to work under pressure<br />\n• English - advanced<br />\n• 2-3+ years of experience providing User Experience and User Interface design solutions for web and/or mobile applications.<br />\n• Solid experience in wireframes, workflows, prototypes, and personas<br />\n• Excellent knowledge of User Centered Design process and usability principles<br />\n• Excellent knowledge of web standards, mobile/responsive design<br />\n• Strong knowledge in conducting user research and usabililty testing<br />\n• Strong User Interface skills (design patterns, iconography, imagery production, etc)<br />\n• Solid design foundation (typography, grids, colour theories, design principles)<br />\n• Competency in standard design tools (Adobe Creative Suite, Visio, Axure, Balsamiq, etc)<br />\n• Good knowledge and understanding of web technologies (HTML, CSS, jQuery, Javascript, etc...)</dd></dl><div class=\"subtitle-line\"><a name=\"section3\" ></a><h3>Advertiser</h3></div><dl class=\"details\"><dt>Brief description of the company</dt><dd>NESS KDC, Ltd. ( Ness Development Center Košice ), opened in 2005, is the first succesful independent base of European strategy of Ness in the area of software engineering. Research and Development Center in Košice is a part of the global delivery organisation Ness Technologies which thanks to the succesful SPL ( Software Product Lab) belongs to the worldwide leaders in the area. <br />\n<br />\nNESS KDC, Ltd. achieves strategic goals worldwide by means of combination of provided services. These are for example design and development of solutions, product testing, provision and maintenance of their quality, implementation of new solutions, technical support of the extensive applications, project management and many more.<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nhttp://www.nesskdc.sk</dd><dt>Main focus of the company's activities</dt><dd><span itemprop='industry'>Information Technology</span></dd><dt>Number of employees</dt><dd>250-499 employees</dd><dt>Company address</dt><dd itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/PostalAddress\"><b>NESS KDC, s.r.o.<br /></b>Business Center Moldavská, Moldavská 10/B <a rel='no-follow' itemprop='map' id=\"id-show-map3\" title=\"Show in map\" class=\"ico show-on-map active\" href=\"/show_map.php?action=contact&amp;offer_id=2276947&amp;geo_id=192151\">Show in map</a><br />040 11 Košice<br /><a  rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"new\" style=\"color:black\" href=\"http://www.nesskdc.sk\">http://www.nesskdc.sk</a><br /></dd><dt>Contact</dt><dd itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ContactPoint\">Contact person: Mgr.  Andrea Takáčová<br />E-mail: <a title=\"E-mail CV to the company using an online form\" rel='nofollow' target=\"_blank\" href=\"/redirect.php?sendcv_offer_id=2276947&amp;inc_stat=1&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fnessjobs.redmatch.com%2FEurope%2FCandidates%2FPosition23456\"><script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ndocument.write(''  + '&#99;' + '&#97;' + '&#114;' + '&#101;' + '&#101;' + '&#114;' + '&#64;' + '&#110;' + '&#101;' + '&#115;' + '&#115;' + '&#107;' + '&#100;' + '&#99;' + '&#46;' + '&#115;' + '&#107;');\n// -->\n</script>\n</a><br /></dd></dl><div class=\"row space-on-bottom\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"small red button nice radius button-apply track-event-button \"  target=\"_blank\" href=\"/redirect.php?sendcv_offer_id=2276947&amp;inc_stat=3&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fnessjobs.redmatch.com%2FEurope%2FCandidates%2FPosition23456\">Send CV to the company</a></div></div><div class=\"line-separator clear\"></div><div class=\"space-on-bottom\"><b>ID: </b>2276947 &nbsp; <b>Dátum zverejnenia: </b><span itemprop='datePosted'>6.10.2015</span><div class=\"row hide-on-phones\"><b>Lokalita: </b><a href=\"/praca/kosic